{"tid":1582348,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"白宮中國顧問白邦瑞：關稅可加至50%或100%","createTime":"2019-09-20T04:20:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-20T04:25:17.000Z","uid":41404,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"925ca4d618563cc032ce83221645ab439c6bdcf6","tid":1582348,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T04:20:46.000Z","msg":"白宮中國政策顧問白邦瑞（Michael Pillsbury）接受《南華早報》訪問，他認為美國總統特朗普擁有讓貿易戰升級的選項，關稅可以加得更高，可從現時低水平加至50%或100%。白邦瑞亦指，特朗普擁有很大範圍的選項，包括涉及金融市場、華爾街。<br />\n<br />\n對於批評指特朗普警告全力打貿易戰只是虛張聲勢，白邦瑞指這是錯誤。特朗普在貿易領域給中國帶來的壓力顯著受到限制。<br />\n<br />\n對於美國會否將香港持續的示威，作為貿易戰談判條件，白邦瑞指特朗普沒煽動香港示威者的行動，幕後黑手的講法被證實是錯誤。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190920/60064326\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190920%2F60064326&d=56TVgGSmQeZ0yTrvrOoz8u9tl09raJ%2B2zMWOssuGUT0%3D&h=c26b027a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190920%2F60064326&h=6928dd7a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190920/60064326</a>"},{"pid":"a8c750838630fe674728916db3cdd5b43a129cbe","tid":1582348,"uid":193215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T04:22:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係時候要focus返行動post，做多啲文宣<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1582170\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1582170</a>"},{"pid":"f9e3cef8046531ebd7105bc75e1016726248e8f6","tid":1582348,"uid":277845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T04:25:17.000Z","msg":"9.29全球反極權集會 聲援維吾爾人 香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoh